503
00:19:05,041 --> 00:19:06,500
Oh. It is early,

504
00:19:06,583 --> 00:19:09,291
but if you wanted me to meet
your parents, I'd be willing.

505
00:19:09,375 --> 00:19:10,333
[KIMITO]
Huh?

506
00:19:11,666 --> 00:19:14,208
It appears that your
undershirt is cut as well.

507
00:19:14,291 --> 00:19:15,208
Yeah, you're right.

508
00:19:15,291 --> 00:19:16,708
Then I'll have
to sew that, too.

509
00:19:16,791 --> 00:19:18,708
Take off your shirt,
please. Quickly.

510
00:19:18,791 --> 00:19:20,458
What? No, that's okay.

511
00:19:20,541 --> 00:19:21,833
Just do it!

512
00:19:21,916 --> 00:19:23,500
[KIMITO] If I give you my shirt,
I'll be half-naked.

513
00:19:23,583 --> 00:19:24,541
[KAREN gasps]

514
00:19:26,708 --> 00:19:29,166
That's part of my master plan!

515
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:31,625
[KIMITO yelling]

516
00:19:34,041 --> 00:19:36,083
You're not hurt, are you?

517
00:19:36,166 --> 00:19:37,125
No...

518
00:19:38,541 --> 00:19:39,500
Good.

519
00:19:44,458 --> 00:19:46,208
[KAREN]
You have peculiar limbs.

520
00:19:46,291 --> 00:19:47,541
[KIMITO]
Do I?

521
00:19:47,625 --> 00:19:50,333
They're not like
any girl's I've seen.

522
00:19:50,416 --> 00:19:51,666
But I don't get it.

523
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:54,000
They aren't all that much
larger than mine, so...

524
00:19:54,083 --> 00:19:56,291
So then how is it that
you're able to overpower me

525
00:19:56,375 --> 00:19:58,041
with such ease?

526
00:19:58,125 --> 00:20:00,916
It really is
pointless, isn't it?

527
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,958
I always wanted
to be a swordsman.

528
00:20:04,041 --> 00:20:07,041
From the start of my youth,
all I did was train to fight.

529
00:20:07,125 --> 00:20:08,875
Maybe I was wasting my time.

530
00:20:08,958 --> 00:20:10,500
I am a girl, after all.

531
00:20:10,583 --> 00:20:12,291
Why try?

532
00:20:12,375 --> 00:20:14,041
[KIMITO]
Don't say that.

533
00:20:14,125 --> 00:20:15,541
Kagurazaka?

534
00:20:15,625 --> 00:20:18,041
You've worked your butt
off and it shows, Karen.

535
00:20:18,125 --> 00:20:20,666
So what if you're a girl.
You can do anything you want.

536
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:22,333
Not to mention, you're one
of the strongest people

537
00:20:22,416 --> 00:20:23,875
I've ever seen!

538
00:20:23,958 --> 00:20:25,541
I'm always impressed
by your work ethic

539
00:20:25,625 --> 00:20:28,250
and your dedication
to your craft.

540
00:20:28,333 --> 00:20:30,166
Seeing someone
train as hard as you?

541
00:20:30,250 --> 00:20:31,541
And never give up?

542
00:20:31,625 --> 00:20:33,291
That's a beautiful thing.

543
00:20:36,166 --> 00:20:37,958
You're serious, right?

544
00:20:38,041 --> 00:20:40,333
You aren't gonna start laughing.

545
00:20:40,416 --> 00:20:42,916
You really...
think I'm beautiful.

546
00:20:44,166 --> 00:20:45,541
Ready or not!

547
00:20:47,166 --> 00:20:49,416
[REIKO]
It appears to be empty.

548
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:50,500
But I'm not crazy.

549
00:20:50,583 --> 00:20:51,541
You heard 'em say they saw him

550
00:20:51,625 --> 00:20:53,791
going into Karen's room,
too, right?

551
00:20:53,875 --> 00:20:56,083
[REIKO] Yes, but where
on earth did they go?

552
00:20:56,166 --> 00:20:57,125
[AIKA]
Beats me.

553
00:20:57,208 --> 00:20:58,625
Okay, look.

554
00:20:58,708 --> 00:21:00,833
There's no reason to hide,
we're not doing anything wrong.

555
00:21:01,875 --> 00:21:03,750
[KIMITO yelps]

556
00:21:03,833 --> 00:21:05,708
Don't move or
they'll hear us in here!

557
00:21:05,791 --> 00:21:06,875
I don't know how
you can say that

558
00:21:06,958 --> 00:21:08,125
in our current position!

559
00:21:08,208 --> 00:21:10,708
Hey! I told you not to move!

560
00:21:10,791 --> 00:21:12,041
[KIMITO yells]

561
00:21:12,125 --> 00:21:15,083
No... Stop. Not there!

562
00:21:15,166 --> 00:21:16,125
[KAREN gasps]

563
00:21:19,250 --> 00:21:20,541
[ALL gasp]

564
00:21:20,625 --> 00:21:23,833
--[AIKA] Kimito!
--[REIKO] Oh, Kimito!

565
00:21:23,916 --> 00:21:24,833
What is this?

566
00:21:24,916 --> 00:21:26,750
What were you two
doing in there?

567
00:21:27,125 --> 00:21:32,375
[music playing, MEN grunting]

568
00:21:32,458 --> 00:21:33,625
Oh, boy.

569
00:21:33,708 --> 00:21:35,916
I... I was just...

570
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,958
Telling Karen's fortune!

571
00:21:38,041 --> 00:21:38,875
[AIKA]
Huh...

572
00:21:38,958 --> 00:21:39,708
[KIMITO]
Huh?

573
00:21:39,791 --> 00:21:42,083
Is that all? Oh!

574
00:21:42,166 --> 00:21:45,541
In that case,
you'd better finish up!

575
00:21:45,625 --> 00:21:47,708
[MALE VOICE 8B]
"Tap out! Now!"

576
00:21:48,250 --> 00:21:50,666
Stop stalling and
tell her fortune already!

577
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:51,625
Go on!

578
00:21:51,708 --> 00:21:53,000
"You got me mad now."

579
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:54,250
What's takin' so long?

580
00:21:54,333 --> 00:21:56,125
[KIMITO growling]

581
00:21:56,208 --> 00:21:57,458
[KIMITO]
"You got me mad now!"

582
00:21:57,541 --> 00:21:59,125
[AIKA] The heck do you mean,
"I got you mad now?"

583
00:21:59,208 --> 00:22:00,083
Tell the fortune!

584
00:22:00,166 --> 00:22:01,916
[KIMITO]
"You got me mad now!"

585
00:23:32,833 --> 00:23:34,083
The secret ingredient.

586
00:23:34,166 --> 00:23:35,041
A little love.

587
00:23:35,125 --> 00:23:36,416
You nasty pervert!

588
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:38,833
I'm nervous! I've never been
a maidservant before!

589
00:23:38,916 --> 00:23:40,291
Do it right now or else!

590
00:23:40,375 --> 00:23:42,416
You sound like
a dying wildebeest!

591
00:23:42,500 --> 00:23:43,875
[HAKUA]
Will you gather sand too?

592
00:23:43,958 --> 00:23:46,750
Sugar and some love!

